OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother fine start and soon
OL,6,Ffeeling very warm in the sunshine.
OL,7,FSome patchy cloud likely developing
OL,8,Ffrom the west during the afternoon,
OL,9,Fwith perhaps some rain or showers
OL,10,Ffurther inland. Risk of some low cloud
OL,11,Ftowards the coast later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVariable cloud overnight and
OL,14,Fmild, with perhaps a few showers in
OL,15,Fthe far southeast and a low risk of
OL,16,Fthunder. A few patches of mist or fog
OL,17,Fpossible by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
